{"tid":619027,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Oldnewsisso唔識串】接個Smartone來電要畀$1080？","createTime":"2018-04-06T09:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T09:40:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6f343d1bad109468b2198bc4b1ce9e2f1947f48b","tid":619027,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T09:40:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180406/20353788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180406%2F20353788&d=67u78jAmP1v6%2FJ%2BZBBJOn2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=75c05ad8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180406%2F20353788&h=d0c52f6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180406/20353788</a><br />\n<br />\n【Old news is so唔識串】<br />\n接個Smartone來電要畀$1080？<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n繼傳出有不法份子利用WhatsApp截取認證碼「騎劫」用家帳號騙財後，網上流傳市民若接聽「93463931」這電話號碼來電，數碼通將收取1,080元通話費，呼籲市民不用接聽。數碼通回覆《蘋果》查詢時澄清，從未有發出相關訊息予客戶，呼籲客戶如收到任何可疑訊息應提高警覺，並致電客戶服務熱線28802688查詢。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，早於2015年WhatsApp就曾流傳過類似訊息，當時有人指「3香港」將向接聽某個「9」字頭電話來電的用戶，收取108元通話費，當時「3香港」已澄清有關訊息屬捏造，並保留法律追究權利。近日類似的假訊息再次在網上「借屍還魂」，facebook更有人將假消息連同騙徒「騎劫」WhatsApp的相片截圖以及警方通知一起傳閱試圖增加何信性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》沙士15周年系列網站，正式登場：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/sars15/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fsars15%2F&d=67u78jAmP1v6%2FJ%2BZBBJOn2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=c0248f92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fsars15%2F&h=1028b085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/sars15/</a>"}]}